org.apache.hadoop.fs

接口 StorageStatistics.CommonStatisticNames

  • 封闭类:
    StorageStatistics

    public static interface StorageStatistics.CommonStatisticNames
    These are common statistic names. The following names are considered general and preserved across different StorageStatistics classes. When implementing a new StorageStatistics, it is highly recommended to use the common statistic names. When adding new common statistic name constants, please make them unique. By convention, they are implicitly unique: - the name of the constants are uppercase, words separated by underscores. - the value of the constants are lowercase of the constant names.
